description: Russia's cases jump by 10,633 in one day, as Moscow's mayor warns the peak is yet to come.
title: Coronavirus: Russia's cases rise by 10,000 in one-day record
title_page: Coronavirus: Russia's cases rise by 10,000 in one-day record - BBC News
maintext: Still, the virus is spreading more quickly now in Russia's regions - where hospital facilities are far worse than in the capital and where medics have been complaining they don't have the masks and protective clothing to keep them safe.
